OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FJersey's Chief Minister Designate,
OL,7,FSenator Lyndon Farnham, has proposed a
OL,8,Fmajor revamp of his Council of
OL,9,FMinisters.
OL,11,FHalf of the current team is out, with
OL,12,Fjust four ministers asked to keep
OL,13,Ftheir current roles.
OL,15,FSome change was expected, given that
OL,16,Fthree of the Council members lost
OL,17,Ftheir seats in June's election, while
OL,18,FConstable Andy Jehan and Deputy
OL,19,FKirsten Morel made it clear during the
OL,20,Felection campaign that they did not
OL,21,Fwant to keep their ministerial roles.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
