OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FMost of the suggestions are
OL,7,Findependents, with only one nominated
OL,8,Fminister who is a member of Reform
OL,9,FJersey - the island's largest party -
OL,10,Fand one that supports the new
OL,11,Fpolitical movement Value Jersey.
OL,13,FElection poll topper Senator Helen
OL,14,FMiles has been put forward as Justice
OL,15,Fand Home Affairs Minister, replacing
OL,16,FSenator Mary Le Hegarat, who is
OL,17,Fproposed as Environment Minister.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FSenator Miles had been expected to
OL,7,Fchallenge Senator Farnham for the top
OL,8,Fjob, but she instead nominated him to
OL,9,Fcontinue as the island's Chief
OL,10,FMinister following "positive and
OL,11,Fconstructive discussions" between them
OL,12,F- he was elected unopposed.
OL,14,FSenator Alan MacLean is asked to enter
OL,15,Fgovernment as the Treasury and
OL,16,FResources Minister after campaigning
OL,17,Fon promises to cut waste in public
OL,18,Fspending.
OL,20,FHe previously held the role for four
OL,21,Fyears between 2014 and 2018.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FSenator MacLean would replace Senator
OL,7,FElaine Millar, who is proposed as
OL,8,FSocial Security Minister.
OL,10,FSenator Ian Gorst is proposed to keep
OL,11,Fhis position as External Relations
OL,12,FMinister, but there will be a new
OL,13,FSustainable Economic Development
OL,14,FMinister, with Deputy Gerald Voisin
OL,15,Fsuggested as Deputy Morel's
OL,16,Freplacement.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
