FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FThe businessman has returned to the
OL,7,FStates after more than two decades
OL,8,Faway and ran on a promise to "make
OL,9,FJersey more affordable, restore
OL,10,Ffinancial discipline, and grow the
OL,11,Feconomy".
OL,13,FSenator Tom Binet is asked to stay on
OL,14,Fas Health and Social Services Minister
OL,15,Fas he continues to lead the project to
OL,16,Fbuild Jersey's new hospital at
OL,17,FOverdale.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
