PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FIf the development were to run to
OL,7,Fschedule, he would still need to win
OL,8,Fanother election to see it through,
OL,9,Fwith Senator Farnham confirming to ITV
OL,10,FNews last week that it should be
OL,11,Fcompleted by the end of 2030.
OL,13,FReform Jersey Deputy Catherine Curtis
OL,14,Fis put forward to take her first
OL,15,Fgovernment ministerial position as
OL,16,FEducation and Lifelong Learning
OL,17,FMinister.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
