OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FShe would replace her party colleague,
OL,7,FRob Ward, who lost his challenge to be
OL,8,Fthe Constable of St Helier in the
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FDeputy Malcolm Ferey is asked to take
OL,12,Fover from Reform Jersey leader Sam
OL,13,FMezec as Housing Minister, after Mr
OL,14,FMezec lost in his bid to become
OL,15,FSenator earlier this month.
OL,17,FIt would be the former Assistant Chief
OL,18,FMinister's first ministerial position.
OL,26,@uD@BrrvD@Brr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
