OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FElsewhere, Constable Jehan's proposed
OL,7,Freplacement as Infrastructure Minister
OL,8,Fis St Brelade Deputy Jonathan Renouf.
OL,10,FConstable Richard Vibert is asked to
OL,11,Fcontinue as Children and Families
OL,12,FMinister, while Deputy Carolyn Labey
OL,13,Fis nominated to keep her role of
OL,14,FInternational Development Minister.
OL,16,FA new position has also been created,
OL,17,Fwith Senator Mark Boleat put forward
OL,18,Fas Planning and Regulation Minister.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FThe office will focus on "reducing
OL,7,Funnecessary bureaucracy and costs,
OL,8,Fwhile supporting economic growth".
OL,10,FHowever, the election for this role
OL,11,Fwill not take place until Tuesday 14
OL,12,FJuly, as an Order is required first
OL,13,Funder Jersey law.
OL,15,FThe rest of Senator Farnham's
OL,16,Fnominations will be debated and voted
OL,17,Fon this Monday (29 June), when others
OL,18,Fwill have the chance to put themselves
OL,19,Fforward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FUncontested candidates will still be
OL,7,Frequired to answer questions from the
OL,8,FAssembly for up to 20 minutes.
OL,10,FStates Members will vote on each
OL,11,Fposition before the Council of
OL,12,FMinisters is formally appointed.
OL,14,FAssistant Ministers will then be
OL,15,Fannounced shortly afterwards.
OL,17,FSenator Farnham's nominations for the
OL,18,FCouncil of Ministers:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782487105
OL,3,CMajor overhaul of Jersey ministers
OL,4,Cproposed
OL,6,FSenator Farnham says: "These
OL,7,Fnominations bring together a team that
OL,8,Freflects the new Assembly and draws on
OL,9,Fthe diverse skills, perspectives and
OL,10,Fexperience of its members.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank colleagues for
OL,13,Ftheir support, guidance and patience
OL,14,Fin compiling this list.
OL,16,F"I very much look forward to working
OL,17,Fwith all members of the new Assembly
OL,18,Fover the coming term."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
